data.description: Indulge in luxury and eco-conscious living within this artist's haven featuring mid-century architecture. Revel in the chef's dream kitchen, adorned with stainless steel appliances and sleek European cabinets. Immerse yourself in sophistication with vinyl flooring and bask in the comfort of the new air conditioning system. High ceilings with exposed beams showcase the home's unique character. Embrace sustainability with impact windows, solar panels, and a water filtration system. An oasis of modern elegance and thoughtful design awaits – your canvas for inspired living. Nestled on an expansive lot, this artistic retreat boasts proximity to premier beaches—Miami Beach and Haulover Beach—offering the perfect blend of serene suburban living just minutes away from vibrant nightlife.
